{"tid":2195907,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《薩爾達無雙 災厄啟示錄》11月上市！重回《曠野之息》百年前的大災厄戰場","createTime":"2020-09-09T12:56:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T00:24:11.000Z","uid":318952,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0b16f33b2550106ac0f54dc65aa173809357c7ed","tid":2195907,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:56:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/09/09/204358_1e5caa22e7f29b57dfe2d35ee0316e09.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F09%2F09%2F204358_1e5caa22e7f29b57dfe2d35ee0316e09.jpeg&h=407656f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n任天堂昨（8）日閃電宣布薩爾達系列最新作品《Zelda無雙 災厄啟示錄》（ゼルダ無双 厄災の黙示録），也是薩爾達無雙系列的第二作，由大家熟悉的光榮特庫摩開發製作。與前作不同的是，本作為《曠野之息》前傳性質的正統續作，將帶玩家回到百年前的海拉魯，親臨戰場；除了林克外，也可以操作公主與四英傑。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NtB-BnB6FrE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNtB-BnB6FrE&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg4MLxsd%2B2XAbZoZSjzCx9%2B0%3D&h=bf982dd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NtB-BnB6FrE</a><br />\n在《曠野之息》故事中，林克醒來已是百年後，還失去記憶，人事已非，玩家只能從冒險中拼湊過往的歷史。雖然說劇情上是前傳，卻也是另一種補完的後日談。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z6gQub3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ6gQub3.jpg&h=8b53a32f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（見到呢幕已經濕咗）<br />\n本作也強調重現《曠野之息》的世界觀，並可以操作林克、薩爾達還有四英傑米法、力巴爾、達爾克爾與烏爾波札，原作中巨大的神獸也會登場。不過戰鬥關卡會如何呈現（無縫地圖或是區域關卡），目前尚未揭露。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ts4l2lqzVLc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fts4l2lqzVLc&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg4MLxsd%2B2XAbZoZSjzCx9%2B0%3D&h=71677f81\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ts4l2lqzVLc</a><br />\n《Zelda無雙 災厄啟示錄》預計在今年11月20日上市，支援中文。<br />\n<br />\n2021 年是《薩爾達傳說》35 週年，同時也是《薩爾達傳說：天空之劍》上市 10 週年，許多玩家都很期待任天堂明年是否會有什麼動作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FhmXTGE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFhmXTGE.jpg&h=a7c4d45e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目前已公開的《薩爾達傳說 曠野之息》續作上市日期仍是「未定」；而在 2018 年舉行的《薩爾達傳說》交響音樂會上，製作人青沼英二曾暗示過有機會推出 Switch 版《薩爾達傳說：天空之劍》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TM2cHzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTM2cHzz.jpg&h=75ecda6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國外網友發現，線上購物平台「英國亞馬遜（Amazon UK）」突然上架了 Nintendo Switch 版《薩爾達傳說：天空之劍》的預購頁面，該頁面顯示售價為 69.99 英鎊（約新台幣 2600 元），其他相關訊息皆未列出。"},{"pid":"dc45d60a30aed8c8e0fb412e1622c282f94b7ca5","tid":2195907,"uid":318952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:57:08.000Z","msg":"大家仲有冇玩薩以達？"},{"pid":"2980fc49b1c3782cc0b372229f06c4b15fce5e30","tid":2195907,"uid":318952,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T12:57:47.000Z","msg":"無雙玩法好似有啲尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d623f37138b7030a32565bfcea755e516fa875","tid":2195907,"uid":318952,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vnb5h90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVnb5h90.jpg&h=265996a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個吸引"},{"pid":"6e24cd044865fb80e51d45063706bd0fab3e640b","tid":2195907,"uid":55493,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:02:38.000Z","msg":"有單機雙打先買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"336e655a28138e692d2cdcdbf539f61b036973b4","tid":2195907,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:02:56.000Z","msg":"P牌功能我DLLM"},{"pid":"07d644aa5b67a9b93896f97449a6ed4120527ff1","tid":2195907,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e24cd044865fb80e51d45063706bd0fab3e640b","tid":2195907,"uid":55493,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:02:38.000Z","msg":"有單機雙打先買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T13:03:35.000Z","msg":"支持單機2play"},{"pid":"eb548b6856d71e5c4aa4c93963dfcb47d11469